                        tool. Nick saw the potential to make <span class="inline-block">Node-RED</span> accessible for enterprise use but knew it would require more
                        enterprise-ready features. FlowFuse was created to elevate Node-RED for enterprise contexts through a <span class="font-medium">secure,
                            professional, and scalable platform</span>.</p>
                    <p><span class="font-medium">FlowFuse seamlessly integrates into existing enterprise environments</span>, offering
                        an adaptable foundation for complex application development. Our customers rely on FlowFuse to develop
