                </div>
                <p class="md:w-[72%] text-justify"><span class="font-medium">We are deeply committed to the success of the Node-RED open
                        source project</span>. Our team dedicates significant effort to developing the core technology of the project
                    and fostering the growth of the Node-RED community. This dedication has helped establish Node-RED as a <span
